{"tid":765021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非永久居民　服刑後遣返內地","createTime":"2018-08-02T12:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T12:21:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b6bdda3304fc330bd701fcdbe331f997c6e91f3","tid":765021,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180802/20466728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F20466728&d=0%2Fn9LnBUZpXCn3HzwSPaesPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=029b132d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F20466728&h=a7efb132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180802/20466728</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月02日 <br />\n<br />\n非永久居民　服刑後遣返內地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180802/large/1533142179_79b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F1533142179_79b5.jpg&h=57073a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次涉嫌賣黃子華黃牛飛的內地男子聲稱透過優才計劃來港定居10年，正在申請永久居民資格，消息人士對本報表示，「法例冇規定住滿7年就要即刻申請永久居民，佢可以決定幾時申請」。如審批期間違法會否影響審批？「當局會考慮申請人係唔係通常居住香港等因素」。由於涉案內地男子以旅客身份來港，一旦被判罪成，服刑之後會被遣返內地，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「如果佢嘅永久居民申請獲批，會另行通知佢來港辦手續」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4,119人經優才計劃定居港<br />\n<br />\n根據優秀人才計劃，旨在吸引來自外地的優才來港定居，提升香港競爭力。年滿18歲、有學士學位、良好品格、語文能力和經濟能力者，可選擇綜合記分制或成就記分制申請。<br />\n<br />\n前者就申請人的年齡、學歷或專業資格、工作經驗、語文能力和家庭背景等評分，最低及格分數為80分，滿分為195分；後者申請人曾獲奧運獎牌、諾貝爾獎、國家/國際獎項等傑出成就獎，或能證明其工作得到同業肯定，若獲認可直接獲滿分195分。<br />\n<br />\n申請需經由特首委任的輸入優秀人才及專才諮詢委員會甄選，獲批者會獲發逗留香港的簽證，如連續7年通常居住香港，可向入境處申請核實永久居民身份資格。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年3月，有4,119人經該計劃獲在港定居，包括體操奧運金牌得主李寧、著名鋼琴家郎朗、內地藝人周迅、章子怡及湯唯等。<br />\n<br />\n■記者謝明明  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n紅館保安：倘警放蛇早可杜絕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅館保安：倘警放蛇早可杜絕<br />\n<br />\n涉炒子華門票還柙　南京來港10年月入2.5萬　IT優才淪黃牛黨<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n大家跟蹤住佢有無獲批"},{"pid":"ae3a5a1cc1292bc8aade31d79f15780c4c0c1a79","tid":765021,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"屍君聾咪一樣落到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a71db4b151f0f6f52bae108ce0ab7fee89b8ba","tid":765021,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ae3a5a1cc1292bc8aade31d79f15780c4c0c1a79","tid":765021,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"屍君聾咪一樣落到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"香港政府根本同支那接哂軌<br />\n<br />\n今時今日仲信既一定要驗下個腦"},{"pid":"0f9b6e6cf981191ccfe030b8ba62fc41497b0981","tid":765021,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"優才計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇嚟係黃牛界嘅新星，香港一定要挽留依啲人材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}